OL,3,CRonaldsway Airport to reduce daily
OL,4,Cclosures in air traffic control ahead
OL,5,Cof TT
OL,7,FStaff at the Isle of Man airport have
OL,8,Fconfirmed there will be a reduction in
OL,9,Fthe number of closures within air
OL,10,Ftraffic control (ATC), ahead of the
OL,11,Fannual TT races.
OL,13,FRonaldsway Airport has faced
OL,14,Fsignificant disruption since September
OL,15,F2023, due to a shortage in qualified
OL,16,FATC staff.
