OL,3,CRonaldsway Airport to reduce daily
OL,4,Cclosures in air traffic control ahead
OL,5,Cof TT
OL,7,FRonaldsway Airport have been contacted
OL,8,Ffor further information regarding the
OL,9,Fupdated closure times.
OL,11,FA lack of air traffic controllers has
OL,12,Fled to daily closures of the runway at
OL,13,FRonaldsway for a couple of years.
OL,15,FIn a Facebook post, a spokesperson for
OL,16,Fthe airport said 'training a new air
OL,17,Ftraffic controller can take between
OL,18,Fthree to four years'.
