OL,3,CRonaldsway Airport to reduce daily
OL,4,Cclosures in air traffic control ahead
OL,5,Cof TT
OL,7,FExperienced controllers coming from
OL,8,Fother airports also require 6-18
OL,9,Fmonths for an Isle of Man
OL,10,Fcertification, allowing them to
OL,11,Foperate within the island.
OL,13,FStaff say the new change will lead to
OL,14,F'fewer disruptions during the day,
OL,15,Fespecially when flights are delayed'.
OL,17,FOther operational updates shared by
OL,18,Fthe airport included updated security
OL,19,Fmeasures.
