OL,3,CRonaldsway Airport to reduce daily
OL,4,Cclosures in air traffic control ahead
OL,5,Cof TT
OL,7,FNew machines will be installed in the
OL,8,Fcoming weeks in the central search
OL,9,Fareas of the main terminal, ensuring
OL,10,Fcompliance with the UK Department for
OL,11,FTransport.
OL,13,FAirport officials say liquids under
OL,14,F100ml must still be placed in a clear
OL,15,Fplastic bag, and laptops must be
OL,16,Fremoved from hand luggage during
OL,17,Fscreening.
